{
  "stem": "12052.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were some news that the-- that existed like Treblinka where they were exterminating the people and so forth.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Only we-- we didn't had any idea of where it will take us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1942.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Approximately May.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we arrived to Deblin in a-- in a-- in cattle cars, and they unloaded us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was a shock.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were screaming and-- and complete chaos.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they loaded our belongings in wagons-- with horse-drawn wagons.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And from the railroad station, where were-- we-- we were going by foot, not by wagon-- only the belonging-- to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was a tremendous experience and shock for us to come to Poland where we had beautiful homes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Poland was a little bit more back with everything, with the style of living.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and the houses and everything-- even the locks-- they were like by us, on barns.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were the door locks where you push.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And the-- the whole thing was gruesome.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So going back, you had to-- we were walking behind the-- behind that horse-drawn wagons.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The Polish people who were delivering things, they were throwing their luggage.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The people were waiting and throwing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they were robbing us right there and there of our belongings.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And you couldn't do nothing while you had the-- you had the German SS.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "If you would step out of the line, they shoot you with no reason.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So lots of people lost their belongings.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And this is what we-- in ghetto there was no work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was-- we were just living from the provisions what we had in food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And a few months-- about two months later-- they were looking for people to go and work on the airport in-- there was one of the big airports in Poland-- military airport.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
